apartaments.title: Luxury Apartment with great views
apartaments.description: Large ocean view Condo in an Italian style Villa, with private pool on your balcony, just steps away from the beach! Located in Samara’s hillside, this property enjoys a breathtaking view on Samara beach and its reef, as well as on lush vegetation just in front of your balcony. The beach is only 2 minutes’ walk and Samara downtown 5 min.This condo offers 3 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, an open kitchen, and a sitting room. The spacious balcony features a dining area, a built-in barbecue and a small pool perfect to cool off after a long beach day while you are preparing a “Parilla” for dinner. Two of the bedrooms have their private entrance and communicate with the living room by the terrace. The main bedroom and living-room have AC. There is also a large laundry/storage room. It's part of a lovely 4 units-Villa built in an Italian style and offers lots of privacy as there is only one neighbor on the left and no direct view. The 2 other condos are down below and can’t be seen from your balcony. You will really feel like you were living in a house! A private parking space is available just in front of your door. Annual fees are reasonable. The property was built in 1988 but has been regularly maintained: roof, fittings, electricity, balcony retaining wall. The plumbing was completely redone at the beginning of 2020. Some interior renovation works will give it a modern touch. There are no many condos for sale in Samara Beach, so don’t wait and schedule a visit now!
